('7179934a-642a-55d9-bccb-785ad96ec688', 'f678a945-afb6-4eeb-a4c6-9728cd1a285d', 'Please refer to the ___ instructions if you have any questions.', '如果你有任何問題，請參考上述的說明。', 'above', 'recent', 'local', 'sudden', '當作形容詞時，表示前述或上文提到的內容。', '在文章中看到 above 即代表在上面提到的內容。', '2026-07-06 12:41:30', '2026-07-06 12:41:30'),
('765d5ff8-86aa-5b85-a2c0-aa4c562cb094', 'd41b197b-4ba6-4de5-a164-d1d0ce9f868e', 'The farmer decided to plant corn on every single ___ of his land to maximize his profit.', '農夫決定在他土地上的每一英畝都種植玉米，以實現利潤最大化。', 'acre', 'century', 'liter', 'degree', 'acre 為名詞，指土地面積單位「英畝」。', 'Acre 唸起來像 ''a car''，想像一輛車可以開過好幾英畝的土地。', '2026-07-06 17:18:40', '2026-07-06 17:18:40'),
('433d7201-6f69-5041-ba7c-7427ba5de25c', '6a3c49a4-a82d-41b8-ba99-aaca2c164044', 'The young scientist''s groundbreaking discovery earned him the ___ of the entire scientific community.', '這位年輕科學家的突破性發現贏得了整個科學界的欽佩。', 'admiration', 'suspicion', 'confusion', 'resentment', 'ad- (朝向) + mir (驚奇/看) + -ation (名詞字尾) → 對某事感到驚奇並注視 → 欽佩。', 'ad (朝向) + mir (看) + ation (名詞) → 朝向某人注視其成就 → 產生欽佩。', '2026-07-06 17:53:16', '2026-07-06 17:53:16'),
('d88551ae-1b1a-5c20-9ec4-07672bb5e184', '440f3037-564b-42f1-8645-74506197969f', 'Please ___ remember to bring your umbrella, as it often rains in this city.', '請___記得帶傘，因為這座城市經常下雨。', 'always', 'quietly', 'quickly', 'beautifully', '由 all (全部) 與 way (道路/方式) 組成。', 'all (全部) + ways (所有方式) → 在所有情況下 → 總是。', '2026-07-06 20:30:10', '2026-07-06 20:30:10'),
('bb906136-28aa-5378-9913-e69e55fac4a0', '8faa3a25-0278-41f9-b36a-52fb72f2e3f7', 'Even though the project is extremely ___, the team is determined to complete it by the end of the year.', '儘管這個計畫非常有野心，團隊仍決心在年底前完成它。', 'ambitious', 'cautious', 'tedious', 'flexible', 'root: ambit (走/圍繞) + -ious (形容詞字尾，表示『充滿...的』) → 想要在範圍內走得很遠，引申為有野心的。', '想像一個人在走 (ambit) 很大範圍的路線，代表他很有野心 (ambitious)！', '2026-07-06 20:43:08', '2026-07-06 20:43:08'),
('fa506157-8c14-5dad-a067-e0172d9a1290', '926df93c-ad5a-4f95-9e93-ba6967ad80c7', 'The ___ arrived at the scene with its sirens wailing to help the accident victims.', '救護車鳴著警笛趕到現場，以幫助事故受害者。', 'ambulance', 'bus', 'truck', 'scooter', '詞根 ambul 意為「行走」或「移動」，ambulance 指的是可以移動的醫療單位。', '想像救護車在街上不斷「移動」(ambulate) 趕往救人的情境來記憶。', '2026-07-06 20:44:01', '2026-07-06 20:44:01'),
('5535b52d-29b9-5640-a28d-04e120cc16b0', '53230321-dab7-4e9e-88de-7cc2a43075ea', 'There are five ___ in the basket.', '籃子裡有五個蘋果。', 'apples', 'books', 'pens', 'toys', 'apple 的複數形式為 apples，表示「多個蘋果」。', '看到數字 five (五) 之後的名詞，記得要加上 s 變成複數型態。', '2026-07-06 14:36:46', '2026-07-06 14:36:46'),
('cb7f4d7d-f2df-524a-b7b1-bf7070877f38', '0197cfc4-ed5f-4990-b4dd-66e83ec8bb46', 'After a long day at work, he loves to sit in a comfortable ___ and read a book.', '在工作了一整天後，他喜歡坐在舒適的扶手椅上讀書。', 'armchair', 'wardrobe', 'bookshelf', 'mirror', '由 arm (手臂) 與 chair (椅子) 組成的複合名詞。', '想像一張椅子長出了兩隻 arm (手臂) 來讓你靠著，那就是 armchair。', '2026-07-06 23:55:54', '2026-07-06 23:55:54'),
('049d007b-121b-5097-a78f-45d901f36e10', '44463e08-f409-4b22-bc75-ee744cd1510a', 'The doctor warned him that a blocked ___ could lead to a serious heart condition.', '醫生警告他，動脈阻塞可能會導致嚴重的問題。', 'artery', 'vein', 'muscle', 'nerve', 'artery 源自希臘語 arteria，意指管狀的構造。', 'artery (動脈) → 想像它是身體裡的『主幹道』，負責將血液送往全身。', '2026-07-07 00:22:13', '2026-07-07 00:22:13'),
('b0258027-56b0-5248-8b36-5afaaf346f2c', '61d272ee-7b99-47db-8cb1-053593def58d', 'The museum is famous for its ___ displays, which attract many young creators.', '這間博物館因其藝術性的展示而聞名，吸引了許多年輕的創作者。', 'artistic', 'scientific', 'musical', 'political', 'art (藝術) + -istic (形容詞字尾，表示「具有...性質的」) → artistic (藝術的)', '記住 artist (藝術家) 的形容詞形式就是 artistic (藝術的)。', '2026-07-07 00:35:10', '2026-07-07 00:35:10'),
('9cbb66a7-4a48-5b4f-90b6-7f402cbec3c0', 'ecf03012-94c8-4be3-add9-d53beb1b790f', 'The entire school gathered in the ___ to watch the graduation ceremony.', '全校師生聚集在禮堂觀看畢業典禮。', 'auditorium', 'laboratory', 'cafeteria', 'library', 'root ''aud'' (聽) → suffix ''-orium'' (場所) = auditorium (禮堂/會堂)', '想像在 auditorium 裡面要用 audio (音訊) 很大聲地聽演講。', '2026-07-07 03:30:55', '2026-07-07 03:30:55'),
('f5ee8d75-5ee0-5fbc-b78a-a51c684c4330', '80d9ef2d-e6ef-49be-9278-b3a6d7117c1e', 'She wears a ___ dress.', '她穿著一件漂亮的洋裝。', 'beautiful', 'thirsty', 'sleepy', 'heavy', 'beauty (美) + ful (充滿...的)', 'beauty (美) + ful (充滿) → 漂亮的', '2026-07-07 02:49:11', '2026-07-07 02:49:11'),
('d851028d-77ae-5602-bb9f-e8a3edf5b150', 'f6caae18-14c9-47e2-8319-ac06318d3f0a', 'She lifted her ___ and looked up at the stars.', '她抬起下巴，仰望著星星。', 'chin', 'nose', 'hand', 'foot', 'chin 為基本名詞，指臉部下方的下巴。', 'chin 讀音像「親」，可以想像親吻下巴的動作來記憶。', '2026-07-07 03:46:44', '2026-07-07 03:46:44'),
('9f1f3973-0441-55f2-bd4a-8dcc550db164', '4bed6b7a-2e60-4168-a3b4-f1eeafa51fcc', 'He is a member of a chess ___.', '他是西洋棋社的成員。', 'club', 'farm', 'sea', 'road', 'club (n.) 意指社團、俱樂部或小團體。', '看到 club 就想到社團，大家聚在一起玩。', '2026-07-07 04:53:11', '2026-07-07 04:53:11'),
('6bfc5d7e-541f-540a-9a61-a44c5849ac3c', '3e484bf5-9600-49c1-8509-468656daef29', 'I have a ___ and a cough, so I need to see a doctor.', '我感冒了而且還在咳嗽，所以我需要去看醫生。', 'cold', 'gift', 'song', 'book', '表示感冒的名詞。', '記住 catch a cold 是「感冒」的意思。', '2026-07-07 05:08:41', '2026-07-07 05:08:41'),
('04140589-691a-5094-bfe9-5c361db90340', '643061ab-f0b0-43f0-8f3e-c5dc634f3094', 'He wants to ___ her this weekend.', '他想這週末跟她約會。', 'date', 'cook', 'sing', 'swim', 'date 作為動詞時，表示「約會」。', 'date 當動詞時，可以聯想兩個人在特定的日期見面，也就是約會。', '2026-07-07 02:47:03', '2026-07-07 02:47:03'),
